	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories THE Merchiston Preparatory Art Expo was held recently in the Reg Evans Hall. Selected boys and parents joined the staff for an evening showcasing their outstanding art. The expo explored the various genres and art techniques used over the past 125 years. The school is incredibly proud of all the boys and their art teachers. - Supplied. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  